Don't you think?

10
00:00:21,206 --> 00:00:22,320
Stop judging me.

11
00:00:22,397 --> 00:00:23,841
I really can't.

12
00:00:23,921 --> 00:00:26,672
- I can't.
- <i>♪ Embrace me ♪</i>

13
00:00:26,749 --> 00:00:28,161
<i>♪ Don't stop ♪</i>

14
00:00:28,377 --> 00:00:31,279
<i>- ♪ We are alive ♪</i>
- Oh.

15
00:00:32,065 --> 00:00:34,642
A brain study revealed that,
when placed in an MRI,

16
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:36,734
a patient's reward center
lit up

17
00:00:36,811 --> 00:00:39,505
when another person sat
in the room.

18
00:00:41,810 --> 00:00:44,029
Neurons fire
when we talk to someone,

19
00:00:44,204 --> 00:00:45,802
think about someone,

20
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:48,460
and they go haywire
when we hold someone's hand.

21
00:00:48,537 --> 00:00:50,005
Come on.
Come on.

22
00:00:50,082 --> 00:00:52,433
<i>♪ Whoo! ♪
♪ Shake, shake ♪</i>

23
